cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is about improving language modeling using Transformers and dynamic evaluation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves neural networks, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing, which could place it in cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as well.
